I"Y<h1 id="1-syncbn-nnsyncbatchnorm">1. ‘SyncBN’: nn.SyncBatchNorm</h1>

<p><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">warning:</code> 当单块GPU训练torch模型时，如果程序内含有<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">SyncBN</code>会报错误: <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">AssertionError: Default process group is not initialized</code></p>

